[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Makes museum-only items worth selling instead of nearly worthless. Configurable multiplier, paid out in the right currency for each item's category.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]Worthwhile sell prices[/b] — vanilla museum items sell for almost nothing. This mod scales them up by a configurable multiplier so duplicates are actually worth offloading.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Currency-aware[/b] — different item categories sell for the right currency (gold, orbs, or tickets) instead of always paying out in coins.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Live config[/b] — adjust the multiplier from the in-game configuration menu and hit "Apply Changes". No restart required, prices update immediately.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/426]Seedify[/url] — plant any crop in any season; pairs well if you're farming for museum items and orbs.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/8]Cheat Enabler[/url] — [font=Courier New]/finditemid[/font] makes tracking down missing museum items dramatically easier.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/37]Easy Living[/url] — among other things, skips the "missing items" dialogue at museum displays.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31]Keep Alive[/url] — required by this mod; keeps everything loaded between play sessions.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30][size=3]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/size][/url]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31][size=3]Keep Alive[/size][/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Compatibility[/b][/size]

[size=3]Built and tested against the latest Steam build of Sun Haven.[/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...\steamapps\common\Sun Haven\BepInEx\plugins[/code][/size]

